name: Habeebah
greetingText: I know your birthday has passed and i couldn't do much for you then cos we weren't really kinda talking then buh i just wanna drop dis!
wishText: I hope your Birthday will always be as beautiful and full of love as you are. You deserve only the best, and I will always wish that for you Happy Birthday In Arrears Lawal Oyindamola yetunde Aduke Habeebah! ;)
